*** mblocFig ***
Theme for postnuke 0.711

AUTHOR

created by J.Wilson / mentalbloc
http://mentalbloc.da.ru

GENERAL

No php files were harmed during the creation of this theme.
No hardcoded colors are used in this theme.

All font calls are CSS based.
via
styles/style.css
styles/styleNN.css

INSTALL

Installation by copying the complete directory structure mblocTec/... etc
to the themes/ directory under postnuke.

EDITING

Please credit me when editing, if you have Adobe ImageReady 3.0
the Graphics are provided in the archive...

ImageReady Save Optimized into the Theme Folder will update the
graphics as required, provided you didn't mess with the slices...

NavBar links are setup via an array in function themeheader()
in theme.php... it should be VERY easy to figure out what's going on.

